snippet.title: Biomes — Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Early Access today by visiting https://www.biomes.gg!

Biomes is a massively-multiplayer browser game where players can team up with friends to build, play, farm, fish, and fight back against the infectious Muck!

Be a part of the community:
Discord: http://discord.gg/biomes
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/biomesgg
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/biomesgg
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/biomesgg
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/hytalegame
